nl.uu.cs.ape.sat.core.solutionStructure

Class ModuleNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.uu.cs.ape.sat.core.solutionStructure.SolutionWorkflowNode
      • nl.uu.cs.ape.sat.core.solutionStructure.ModuleNode

  • public class ModuleNode
extends SolutionWorkflowNode
    The ModuleNode class is used to represent module step in the actual solution workflow. Each ModuleNode represents an action/tool in the solution workflow.

    When compared to the ModuleAutomaton representation of the problem, a Workflow TypeNode correspond to a State of a WorkflowElement.MODULE element.
    Author:
    Vedran Kasalica
